<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type"/>
</head>
<body>
<div style="font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><%= @template_params[:ao_name] %>,</div>
<p style="font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">you have missed the 2pm deadline.</p>

<p style="font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Please <strong>immediately</strong> accept or reject the PQ <strong><%= @template_params[:uin] %></strong></p>
<div style="font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; padding-left:0.5em;margin-left:10px;border-left:4px solid grey;margin-top:5px;margin-right:5px;margin-bottom:5px;">
  <%= @template_params[:question] %>
</div>

<p style="font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Asked by: <%= @template_params[:member_name] %> (<%= @template_params[:house] %>)</p>

<div style="padding-left:0.5em;margin-left:10px;border-left:4px solid black;margin-top:5px;margin-right:5px;margin-bottom:5px;">
  <p style="font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">The link to accept or reject will be in a previous email. <strong>Please search your email inbox for <%= @template_params[:uin] %></strong></p>
</div>

<p style="font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">If you have any questions <a href="mailto:<%= Settings.mail_reply_to %>">Contact the PQ Team</a></p>

<%= render 'shared/mailer/email_signature' %>

</body>
</html>
